---
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<section class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 bg-accent px-16 py-20 w-full">
  <h2 class="font-heading text-[44px] font-bold text-accent-foreground text-center leading-[1.1] tracking-[-1.5px]">
    Want to see if we're<br />the right fit?
  </h2>

  <p class="font-body text-base text-accent-foreground/85 text-center leading-[1.6]">
    Book a free 30-minute discovery call. We'll listen to what you're working on<br />and give you a straight answer on whether we can help. If we can't, we'll tell you that too.
  </p>

  <a href="/contact" class="flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-foreground px-8 py-4 font-heading text-[13px] font-semibold tracking-[1px] text-primary-foreground hover:bg-foreground/90 transition-colors">
    BOOK A FREE DISCOVERY CALL
    <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4" />
  </a>

  <p class="font-body text-sm text-accent-foreground/70 text-center">
    Or check out our <a href="/services" class="underline hover:text-accent-foreground transition-colors">service packages</a> to see what we offer and what it costs.
  </p>
</section>
